2896	resource_create crashes on ValidationErrors with KeyError: 'resources'	seanh		"ckan/logic/action/create.py:resource_create():

    try:
        pkg_dict = _get_action('package_update')(context, pkg_dict)
    except ValidationError, e:
        errors = e.error_dict['resources'][-1]
        raise ValidationError(errors)

This assumes that package_update always returns an error dict with 'resources' in it. This assumption doesn't hold."	defect	new	awaiting triage	ckan-v1.8.1	ckan				ckan	none
